title: Marijuana Cigars?
itunes:title: Marijuana Cigars?
description: This week on The Cigar Authority, is Marijuana actually good for you? John Cena Sr and "The Luchador", Jack Torano from Torano Cigars, we light up the pre-release "Amadeus" from Recluse Cigars, and the new "Tattoo" by Tatuaje Cigars.
